thread.title: BRIEF-Sare Prelim FY Net Profit Down At 2.8 Mln Zlotys

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sare Prelim FY Net Profit Down At 2.8 Mln Zlotys
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - SARE SA:
* REPORTED ON WEDNESDAY PRELIM FY REVENUE AT ABOUT 46.0 MLN ZLOTYS VERSUS 41.3 MLN ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* PRELIM FY EBITDA AT ABOUT 5.7 MLN ZLOTYS VERSUS 6.2 MLN ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* PRELIM FY NET PROFIT AT 2.8 MLN ZLOTYS VERSUS 4.0 MLN ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* DECREASE IN EBITDA AND NET PROFIT IS THE EFFECT OF EMPLOYMENT COSTSâ€™ INCREASE IN 2017 BY AROUND 5.9 MLN ZLOTYS YEAR-ON-YEAR
